<p> This chip contains two 12-bit 4MHz DACs.  The chip also contains a isolated opamp 
and resistor segment for testing purposes.  The DAC accepts a 12-bit digital input signal in binary format.  
The output is a 1.4Vpp sine wave of up to 2MHz, centered at 2.25V. </p>
<p>The <a href="report.pdf">project report</a> contains a description
of the project and details of the design and layout. It also contains testing results of the manufactured design.


